@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout3.cshtml";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Companies House Sync";
}

<main class="service-page">
    <div class="service-container">
        <section class="service-hero">
            <div class="service-copy">
                <span class="service-kicker"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> Service Detail</span>
                <h1 class="service-title">Companies House sync that keeps your client records current and dependable.</h1>
                <p class="service-summary">Companies House Sync removes the manual burden of chasing updates across client records. By connecting your portal to Companies House data, the service helps maintain accurate company information, clearer filing visibility, and less repetitive admin for your team.</p>

                <div class="service-tags">
                    <span class="service-tag">Real-time sync</span>
                    <span class="service-tag">Lower admin load</span>
                    <span class="service-tag">Better data accuracy</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-actions">
                    <a class="service-btn service-btn-primary" href="/Contact">Book a demo</a>
                    <a class="service-btn service-btn-secondary" href="/Account/Signup">Start free trial</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-visual">
                <div class="service-visual-frame">
                    <img src="~/finanza-1.0.0/img/Companies House Integration.png" alt="Companies House sync workflow" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-section">
            <div class="service-section-head">
                <span class="service-section-label">What This Service Covers</span>
                <h2>Keep company information aligned without constant manual reconciliation.</h2>
                <p>Manual updates create unnecessary risk, especially when a firm is dealing with large numbers of active companies. This integration supports a cleaner process by reducing duplicate entry and helping your dashboard reflect current Companies House data more reliably.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-split">
                <article class="service-panel">
                    <h3>How it helps</h3>
                    <p>Your staff can spend less time checking whether company details are current and more time working on client service and compliance. The sync supports a more efficient operating model with fewer avoidable discrepancies.</p>
                    <p>It also improves confidence in the data your firm uses for deadline tracking, portfolio reviews, and day-to-day operational decisions.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="service-panel is-soft">
                    <h3>Included capabilities</h3>
                    <ul class="service-checklist">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Secure API connection to Companies House records</span></li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Automatic sync of company profile information</span></li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Up-to-date status visibility inside your portal</span></li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Cleaner data flow saved directly into your dashboard</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-section">
            <div class="service-cards">
                <article class="service-card">
                    <span class="service-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-keyboard"></i></span>
                    <h3>Less rekeying</h3>
                    <p>Reduce repetitive manual entry and free your team from routine data maintenance work.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="service-card">
                    <span class="service-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i></span>
                    <h3>Cleaner records</h3>
                    <p>Maintain more consistent client data across your portal and reduce the risk of outdated information.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="service-card">
                    <span class="service-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                    <h3>Reliable oversight</h3>
                    <p>Work from stronger data confidence when reviewing companies, planning filings, and checking compliance status.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-section">
            <div class="service-band">
                <div>
                    <h2>Need a cleaner connection to Companies House data?</h2>
                    <p>We can help you set up a more dependable sync process for deadline tracking and record management.</p>
                </div>
                <a class="service-btn service-btn-secondary" href="/Contact">Contact our team</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>
